OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FROH bans audience member   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor heckling child actor   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Royal Opera House has banned an    
OL,6, audience member for life for booing and
OL,7, heckling a 12-year-old actor during a  
OL,8, production of Handel's opera Alcina.   
OL,10,FMalakai M Bayoh was met with cries of  
OL,11,F"Rubbish!" while singing his lines, on 
OL,12,FTuesday, opening night, in London.     
OL,14,FOnlookers shushed the heckler, who left
OL,15,Fsoon after, and loudly applauded Bayoh.
OL,17,FThe ROH said it was "appalled" at the  
OL,18,Foutburst and praised the classically   
OL,19,Ftrained youngster for his well reviewed
OL,20,Fportrayal of Oberto.                   
